channel.title: No-Ip/Other !HELP!
channel.description:
Ok, so I have a server that I've been working on. When I finally finished it, I tried to post it on both MoparScape and google. Each one said my server is offline, here is what I have.
-Opened port 43594. -A 2Wire2701HG-B. -Two Ip addresses, (finalvengeance.no-ip.info, vengeance.servegame.com) -My server is running. -I have a DHCP rotating IP address, but I do have the DUC v2.2.1. -There is a place in my router, that lists this "public" IP for my computer : 70.224.xx.xxx
Here is my portforward. [img]http://xe7.xanga.com/05df050613733233572693/m184331641.jpg[/img]
